                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <locus target="#27r"/>
                                    <desc type="Subscription"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ገድሉ፡ ለአባ፡ ገሪማ። ዘአጽሐፈ፡ አቡነ፡
                                        ሃብተ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መድኀኒተ፡ ነፍሱ፡ ለአቤት፡ ዘወሀበ፡ ለደሴተ፡ ጸጋ፡
                                        ለእስጢፋኖስ፡ ለዘ፡ ጸሐፎ, etc. </q>
                                    <q xml:lang="fr" resp="PRS3182ContiRo">Ce livre est le livre des
                                        Actes d'abbā Garimā, qu'a fait écrire l'abuna Habta Gabrʾēl,
                                        afin qu'il serve au salut de l'âme d'Abēt (?) qui l'a donné
                                        à l'île de Dāgā, à Estèves; pour l'a écrit, etc.</q>
                                    <q xml:lang="en">This book is the Book of the Acts of Abbā
                                        Garimā, commissioned by Abuna Habta Gabrʾēl so that it may
                                        serve for the salvation of the soul of Abēt (?), who donated
                                        it to the island of Dāgā, to Estèves; it was written by...,
                                        etc.</q>
                                    <note>Cataloguing this manuscript, <persName
                                            ref="PRS3182ContiRo"/> interpreted this note as an
                                        explicit, but since, however, it is different from
                                        manuscript to manuscript and thus does not seem belonging to
                                        the main text, it should be rather understood as a
                                        subscription.</note>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="27v"/>
                                    <desc type="Supplication">Supplication to saints </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">እስጢፋኖስ፡ ቀዳሜ፡ ሰማዕት፡ ዘካርያስ፡ ካህን፡ ወዮሐንስ፡ መጥምቅ፡
                                        በእንተ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ወሰማዕት፡ እለ፡ አዕረፉ፡ በሃይማኖት፡ ማቴዎስ፡ወማርቆስ፡ ሉቃን፡
                                        ወዮሐንስ፡ ወንጌላዊያን፡ ማርያም፡ ወለዲታ፡ አምላከ፡ </q>
                                </item>
